# CLAD local configuration for Cline workspace rules
# Copy this file to .cline-clad-config and fill in values for your project.
# .cline-clad-config is gitignored — it is yours alone.
# This file is only for CLAD stage-specific runtime inputs.
# It does NOT configure Cline Auto Compact thresholds or compaction prompts.

## Test command
# The command to run after each implementation edit in CLAD green work.
# Examples:
#   mvn -f reference-impl/java-micronaut-jena/pom.xml test
#   ./gradlew test
#   npm test
TEST_COMMAND=mvn -f reference-impl/java-micronaut-jena/pom.xml test

## Profile storage layer
# The storage technology used by this project's reference-impl profile.
# Examples:
#   Jena TDB2 named graph (Java/Micronaut profile)
#   PostgreSQL schema per concept (Spring Boot profile)
#   MongoDB collection per concept (Node.js profile)
STORAGE_LAYER=Jena TDB2 named graph (Java/Micronaut profile)
